Package com.example.project3

Class Checking

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.Account
com.example.project3.Checking
Direct Known Subclasses:
CollegeChecking
public class Checking extends Account
This class is for a Checking Account that extends the Account class. Calculates monthly interest and fee for a Checking Account.
Author:
Minseok Park, Amogh Sarangdhar
